## STARTUP — READ FIRST
On every new session, BEFORE doing anything else:
1. Run `~/.mnemo-cc/hooks/mnemo-startup.sh` — loads long-term memory from Mnemo Cortex

## SESSION END
Before ending any session:
1. Run: `~/.mnemo-cc/hooks/mnemo-writeback.sh "summary of what happened" "key fact 1" "key fact 2"`
   - Summarize what was done, decisions made, and anything future sessions should know
   - This archives to Mnemo Cortex so you remember it next time
